                            <comment id="13049089" author="slebresne" created="Tue, 14 Jun 2011 09:58:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;MerkleTree.init(), which is used to create the merkle tree in case there is no data, was creating a nonsensical tree by stopping it&apos;s iteration too late.&lt;/p&gt;

